QuickFixLine      -> Search
Boolean           -> Constant
Character         -> Constant
Conditional       -> Statement
Define            -> PreProc
Debug             -> Special
Delimiter         -> Special
Exception         -> Statement
Float             -> Number
Function          -> Identifier
Include           -> PreProc
Keyword           -> Statement
Label             -> Statement
Macro             -> PreProc
Number            -> Constant
Operator          -> Statement
PreCondit         -> PreProc
Repeat            -> Statement
SpecialChar       -> Special
SpecialComment    -> Special
StorageClass      -> Type
String            -> Constant
Structure         -> Type
Tag               -> Special
Typedef           -> Type
# }}}

NvimInternalError -> ErrorMsg

